<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Районное видео</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .header {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            color: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }
        .header h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        .header p { opacity: 0.9; }
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            padding: 0 1rem;
        }
        .upload-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .telegram-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #27A7E7;
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }
        .telegram-btn:hover { transform: scale(1.05); }
        .video-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }
        .video-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }
        .video-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); }
        .video-thumbnail {
            position: relative;
            padding-top: 56.25%;
            background: #f0f0f0;
        }
        .video-thumbnail iframe {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border: none;
        }
        .video-info { padding: 1.5rem; }
        .video-title {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: #333;
        }
        .video-meta {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .video-author { color: #667eea; font-weight: 600; }
        .video-date { color: #999; }
        .stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .stat-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            color: white;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .stat-number { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; }
        .stat-label { opacity: 0.9; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
            padding: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
            .video-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>🎥 НАШЕ РАЙОННОЕ ВИДЕО</h1>
        <p>Смотри и выкладывай видео своего района</p>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="stats">
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-number" id="videoCount">0</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Всего видео</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-number" id="authorCount">0</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Авторов</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-number" id="todayCount">0</div>
                <div class="stat-label">За сегодня</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="upload-card">
            <h2>📤 Хочешь выложить своё видео?</h2>
            <p>Просто отправь его в Telegram бота!</p>
            <a href="https://t.me/thePUBLIcATIONONthewhitetube_bot" class="telegram-btn" target="_blank">
                📱 ОТПРАВИТЬ ВИДЕО
            </a>
            <p style="color: #666; margin-top: 1rem;">
                1. Нажми на кнопку выше<br>
                2. Отправь видео боту<br>
                3. Оно сразу появится здесь!
            </p>
        </div>

        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            <button onclick="showAll()" style="padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 5px; border: none; background: white; cursor: pointer;">🆕 Все</button>
            <button onclick="showToday()" style="padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 5px; border: none; background: white; cursor: pointer;">📅 За сегодня</button>
        </div>

        <div class="video-grid" id="videoGrid">
            <!-- VIDEO_LIST -->
            <!-- Сюда бот будет добавлять видео -->
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        Сделано соседями для соседей ❤️
    </div>

    <script>
        let videos = [];

        function showAll() {
            const grid = document.getElementById('videoGrid');
            grid.innerHTML = videos.map(v => v.html).join('');
        }

        function showToday() {
            const today = new Date().toDateString();
            const grid = document.getElementById('videoGrid');
            const todayVideos = videos.filter(v => new Date(v.date).toDateString() === today);
            grid.innerHTML = todayVideos.map(v => v.html).join('');
        }

        function updateStats() {
            document.getElementById('videoCount').textContent = videos.length;
            const authors = new Set(videos.map(v => v.author));
            document.getElementById('authorCount').textContent = authors.size;
            const today = new Date().toDateString();
            const todayCount = videos.filter(v => new Date(v.date).toDateString() === today).length;
            document.getElementById('todayCount').textContent = todayCount;
        }

        // Загружаем видео при старте
        showAll();
        updateStats();
    </script>
</body>
</html>